## Steps

1. Read `feature_list.json` and identify the next `pending` task
2. Read relevant source files to understand the context
3. Write failing tests first (TDD)
4. Implement the feature to make tests pass
5. Run `{{TEST_RUNNER}}` — confirm green
6. Update `feature_list.json` status to `completed`
7. Append to `claude-progress.txt`
8. Commit changes
